			<div class="article-title col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-8 pv-sm">
				<h1 class="txt-f4 txt-s7 balance-text">Boe Declaration: navigating an uncertain Pacific </h1>
			</div>
			<div class="article-author pv-md col-sm-offset-3 col-sm-6">
															<a class="txt-dn txt-f1 txt-s3 txt-tu" href="/the-interpreter/contributors/articles/anna-naupa">
							Anna Naupa
						</a>
											<a class="txt-dn txt-f1 txt-s3 txt-tu" href="/the-interpreter/contributors/articles/murray-ackman">
							Murray Ackman
						</a>
											<a class="txt-dn txt-f1 txt-s3 txt-tu" href="/the-interpreter/contributors/articles/patrick-tuimalealiifano">
							Patrick Tuimalealiifano
						</a>
												</div>
							<div class="article-summary col-sm-offset-1 col-sm-10">
					<p class="txt-s5 txt-f1 balance-text txt-lmd">
						Leaders agreed on an “expanded concept of security” to cope with threats the Pacific faces today and will face tomorrow.
					</p>
				</div>
					</div>

